    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows clear signs of its history, including several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays moderate wear on the upholstery and high-touch surfaces. Mechanically, it runs well and has been consistently serviced, though a new owner might want to address minor cosmetic issues over time. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
