      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or smudge anywhere! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh new-car smell and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! \u2728 Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
