    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 platform, featuring a naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Meticulously maintained to concours standards, the mechanical integrity is underscored by recent preventative replacement of the rod bearings with VAC coated units and updated throttle actuators. The 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, short-throw shifts, while the factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and M-Variable differential provide surgical precision through corners. This specimen retains its original factory finish with no subframe fatigue or structural deviations, representing a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
